response: Turkey

clue: Theon's greatest work, available online, has mathematics useful for understanding this founder of the Academy

response: Plato

clue: Writing on these, Theon covers, among others, the circular, oblong, prime & even ones

response: numbers

clue: Theon seems to have lived at the same time that this Roman emperor was building his famous wall

